# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

CALC_SCUBA2_FCF - Recipe for calculating FCFs from SCUBA-2 calibrators

=head1 DESCRIPTION

A simple PICARD recipe to calculate the FCF from reduced SCUBA-2
images of calibration sources.

=head1 NOTES

The input data should be uncalibrated.

The results of the calculation are printed to the screen and written
to a log file, C<log.fcf>.

=head1 DISPLAY

No display is used by this recipe.

